<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thusim Lui chuh ei hilh in,
 Chunglam muhloh thusim;
 Isu leh A lopina thu,
 Leh A hehpihna thu;
 Het nuom takin ei hilh in,
 Naupangte hilh bangin;
 Hatlo, gimthei, panpih bei,
 Gitloh a nin ka hi.
 Phuonzak ding

[V2]
 Thusim Lui chuh ei hilh in, (2)
 Thusim Lui chuh ei hilh in,
 Isu hehpihna thu.

[V3]
 2. Thusim Lui chuh ei hilh in,
 Ka lak theihna dingin;
 Tatna maktak chanchin leh,
 Pathien ngaihdamna thu;
 Thusim chuh ei hilh zingin,
 &quot;Zing tunga daichim&quot; kai;
 Suna a hung hul bangin,
 Ka hengilh vak ngala.

[V4]
 3. Aw nem hieucha'n ei hilh in,
 Guntak, tihtakzet in;
 Gilo ka hi hezing in!
 Isu, hukdam ka ngai;
 Thusim chu ei hilh zingin,
 Lungkham, lungzin laia;
 Bangtik ale kei dinga,
 Lungmuonpa chu Na hi.

[V5]
 4. Thusim Lui chuh ei hilh in,
 Khawvel lopina hi;
 Kei di'n bangmah lo ahi,
 Tih haksa ka sak tieng;
 Ahi, khawvel lopina'n,
 Ka thagau a thep tieng
 Thusim Lui chuh ei hilhin,
 Krista hih damna thu.</lyrics>
<title>TELL ME THE OLD, OLD STORY</title>
<hymn_number>246</hymn_number>
</song>